{
  "stem": "25912.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the shortage of food was absolutely appalling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't bake bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You had no fuel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no electricity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a shortage of water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to go to standpipes in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if you were in an area where there were either Germans shooting from the rooftops, many, many people were killed while queuing for water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was pretty hairy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was wearing just what I had worn for six weeks of the Warsaw rising.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No change of clothes at that stage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my shoes were completely cut.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I wore a new pair of shoes, but they were literally cut into strips by all the debris and the ruins we had to walk over during that time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I had a sort of anorak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I saw the first tomatoes, I picked all the tomatoes I could in sight and stuffed them inside the lining of my anorak, which didn't do it much good, I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And got to Pruszkow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were in [NON-ENGLISH] barracks, or whatever they were-- huts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody was saying a different story what they were going to do with us, deporting us to concentration camps, deporting us to Germany for labor, all sorts of stories going around.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I cut my hair then because I hadn't been able to wash it for six weeks, and I had long plaits, which I couldn't even undo.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were so full of dust and debris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I cut my hair with somebody's knife.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the next day, there was a selection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were all lined up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was, again, a lottery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You didn't know where you wanted to be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "See, I was trying to work out what was the best thing to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Old people, young people.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
